========
aiospamc
========

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/azure-devops/build/mjcaley/aiospamc/2/master
    :target: https://dev.azure.com/mjcaley/aiospamc/_build
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/azure-devops/coverage/mjcaley/aiospamc/2/master
    :target: https://dev.azure.com/mjcaley/aiospamc/_build
